{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/About_This_Game.gif?t=1715111749\" /><br>King of the Hat is 2-4 player 2D party platformer where you fight with a hat! Throw your hat to attack, defend and bait opponents. But watch out! If someone jumps on your hat... you die!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/Jump_On_Hats.gif?t=1715111749\" /><br>In King of the Hat, your hat contains your soul. Crush your opponent\u2019s hats (and souls) to assert your dominance over them.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/Fight_With_Hats.gif?t=1715111749\" /><br>When you throw your hat, it goes on fire and becomes invulnerable. You can use it to beat the devil out of other players or to defend against your opponents\u2019 flaming hats.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/Competitive.gif?t=1715111749\" /><br>Although the basic mechanics are easy to pick up and play, King of the Hat allows for deep, hat-tastic competitive play as a 2 player game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/837350/extras/Party.gif?t=1715111749\" /><br>Change the rules, add power ups and play around level hazards to create the hat-based madness you've always dreamed of.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Hatlandia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/837350/6ed284884831922873dcc938c12ff445b7e49b5b.jpg"},{"name":"Hat Noobie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/837350/313db31469879b1e949e89026b51fa8d294db7c0.jpg"},{"name":"Hat Squire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/837350/8efeabefb87c276d